posts.name: Let Me Be
posts.body:
Please let me be angry, it's just what I know.
When I'm angry I speak honestly, that's how it goes.
It's true I wear emotions like I wear my clothes,
they change everyday that's how I speak from my soul.
The pain I feel within is only starting to grow,
I was told to deal with it, don't let that river flow.
'Be the bigger man, you should just let it go.'
When doi get to demand of you the maturity you never show?
When do I get to be right and you have to glow
with the red pang of repentance that I so often chose?
You say you aren't at fault, so lets check your nose.
In my understanding that's called Pinocchio's.
You fucking liar, you traded your fair share of blow's!
I know you just can't help but continuing to sew
insecurities in me, so I'm done, my eyes are closed.
I won't look for your approval, this relationship is a ghost.

posts.name: Desano
posts.body:
Gluten stretch and rebound
Flower caked to the ground
The scent of marinara waft
Voices murmur light and soft
Napoli fa pizza bella
My tastebuds have found their Cinderella

posts.name: Ducks
posts.body:
oh for the courage of a duck
leap and not look back
to put life in the hands of luck

oh for the grace of a koi
simply be
to never apologize for having joy

oh for the memory of buildings
protect the ones you love
holding their secrets in your gilding

oh to be and just be
to know the person I call me
oh for the courage of a duck
